deployedGeneratedSources.name: #utility.yul

checkToken(address).details: Function to check the amount of VT the ad has

params.ad: address of the recipient that wants to check their VT

returns._0: A uint256 representing the amount of VT owned by the msg.sender.

destroyToken(address,uint256).details: Function to destroy a certain amount of VT from an owner

params.tokenAmount: uint256 amount indicating the number of tokens to be destroyed
params.tokenOwner: address of the account whose VT will be destroyed

returns._0: a uint256 representing the number of VT belonging to tokenOwner that was destroyed

getToken(address,uint256).details: Function to give VT to the recipient for a given wei amount

params.recipient: address of the recipient that wants to buy the VT
params.weiAmt: uint256 amount indicating the amount of wei that was passed

returns._0: a uint256 representing the amount of VT bought by the msg.sender.

transferToken(address,uint256).details: Function to transfer the credit from tx.origin to the recipient

params.amt: uint256 aount of VT to transfer
params.recipient: address of the recipient that will gain in VT

transferTokenFrom(address,address,uint25.details: Function to transfer the credit from specified owner to the recipient

params.amt: uint256 aount of VT to transfer
params.from: address of the owner that is giving out token
params.recipient: address of the recipient that will gain in VT
